data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom ranch home located in the heart of Omaha.  This cozy and inviting property features a spacious living room, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with loved ones.  The kitchen boasts ample cabinet space and a convenient layout, making meal prep a breeze.  The 3 bedrooms offer plenty of space for a growing family or guests. Outside, you'll find a large fenced in backyard with room for outdoor activities and a patio for enjoying some sunshine or evening sunsets.  Don't miss the chance to make this lovely ranch home your own in the bustling city of Omaha.
